Hand, Respondent, v. Society for Savings, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 6, 1892.) Appeal from city court, general term. Action by Ell wood S. Hand against Society for Savings in the City of Cleveland.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bisohoff, JJ.

W. M. Stafford, for appellant. O. D. Hart Broum, for respondent. .

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 18 N. Y. Supp. 157.
